Developer

My passion for programming began as a child, thanks to my interest in video games. The idea of working ''behind the scenes'' of a game always intrigued me. So, thanks to a wide range of courses that I attended and the help of some computer experts, I am now working heavily to become a well-known developer.

This site is built without a cms, and hosted completely free. It uses using HTML, Grunt, Sass and Jekyll. The code is on Github. If you want to know more about, see if we can work together and just contact me on the socials.
